The paper deals with image and video processing, specifically background/foreground segmentation, which is a common problem in computer vision and falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions applications such as text extraction, which falls under machine learning (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of robust regression method also suggests the possibility of statistical learning (cs.LG) being involved. Finally, the paper mentions compression of screen content, which could involve data structures (cs.DS) for efficient storage and retrieval.
